```plantuml
@startuml dspace-group_simphera-reference-architecture-azure

actor User
participant "Terraform CLI" as Terraform
participant "Azure Resource Manager" as ARM
participant "Azure Kubernetes Service (AKS)" as AKS
participant "PostgreSQL Flexible Server" as PostgreSQL
participant "MinIO Storage Account" as MinIO
participant "Azure Key Vault" as KeyVault
participant "Azure Virtual Network" as VNet
participant "Log Analytics" as LogAnalytics
participant "Bastion Host" as Bastion

User -> Terraform: Executes terraform apply
Terraform -> ARM: Authenticates & sends deployment request
ARM -> VNet: Creates Virtual Network & Subnets
ARM -> AKS: Provisions Kubernetes Cluster
ARM -> PostgreSQL: Deploys PostgreSQL Flexible Server
ARM -> MinIO: Creates Storage Account for MinIO
ARM -> KeyVault: Provisions Key Vault for secrets
ARM -> LogAnalytics: (Optional) Sets up Log Analytics
ARM -> Bastion: (Optional) Deploys Bastion Host

AKS -> KeyVault: Retrieves secrets (kubeconfig, credentials)
PostgreSQL -> KeyVault: Stores/retrieves database credentials
MinIO -> KeyVault: Manages storage access keys
Bastion -> VNet: Provides secure access to private resources

User <-- Terraform: Returns outputs (kubeconfig, endpoints)
User -> AKS: Deploys SIMPHERA applications
AKS -> PostgreSQL: Connects to database
AKS -> MinIO: Uses object storage
AKS -> LogAnalytics: (Optional) Sends monitoring data

@enduml
```